text: Audun Rusten (11 June 1894 - 14 December 1957) was a Norwegian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Norwegian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Norway Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bergen Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
